<plot>Amongst thunder and lightning God creates a man. He descends on earth as a boy scout and as his first job he helps an old woman across the extremely busy street. Not even completing the task, he jumps on a fire-engine helping to put out a fire and becomes a fireman, only to be a doctor in an operation room the next second. As his journey continues he finds in himself in more and more familiar situations. Can the boy scout make a profound impact on world society or will society only get hold of him?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?011147</url></doc>
